section.text:

  Section 487 of the Higher Education Act of 1965 (
  20 U.S.C. 1094
) is amended—

clause.text:
the terms bank and savings association have the definition given those terms, respectively, under 
                    section 3 of the Federal Deposit
			 Insurance Act (
                    12 U.S.C. 1813
                  );

the term credit union means a Federal credit union and a State credit union as those terms are defined, respectively,
			 under 
                    section 101 of the Federal Credit Union Act (
                    12 U.S.C. 1752
                  );
